To implement the requested functionality, I will modify `lib.rs` to store the codon-to-amino-acid mappings and implement the matching logic based on the IUPAC shorthand notation.

Here are the changes:
1.  **`CodonsInfo` struct**: Removed the `phantom` field and added a `pairs` field to store the provided codon/name mappings.
